file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  license:
    name: GPL 2.0
  title: Home Unite Us
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://homeunite.us/api
paths:
  /serviceProviders:
    $ref: './paths/serviceProviders.yaml'
  /serviceProviders/{providerId}:
    $ref: './paths/serviceProvider.yaml'
  /auth/signup:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authSignup.yaml'
  /auth/signin:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authSignin.yaml'
  /auth/confirm:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authConfirm.yaml'
  /auth/signout:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authSignout.yaml'
  /auth/token:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authToken.yaml'
  /auth/session:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authSession.yaml'
  /auth/refresh:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authRefresh.yaml'
  /auth/forgot_password:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authForgotPassword.yaml'
  /auth/confirm_forgot_password:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authConfirmForgotPassword.yaml'
  /auth/user:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authUser.yaml'
  /auth/private:
    $ref: './paths/auth/authPrivate.yaml'
components:
  securitySchemes:
      jwt:
        type: http
        scheme: bearer
        bearerFormat: JWT
        x-bearerInfoFunc: openapi_server.controllers.security_controller.requires_auth
  responses:
    $ref: './responses/_index.yaml'
  parameters:
    $ref: './parameters/_index.yaml'
  schemas:
    $ref: './schemas/_index.yaml'
    ApiResponse:
      example:
        code: 0
        type: type
        message: message
      properties:
        code:
          format: int32
          title: code
          type: integer
        type:
          title: type
          type: string
        message:
          title: message
          type: string
      title: ApiResponse
      type: object

Error:
unmarshal: yaml: unmarshal errors:
